WITH category_items AS (
    SELECT 
        COALESCE(c.name, 'Uncategorized') AS category_name,
        oi.item_id,
        oi.quantity
    FROM order_items oi
    JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
    LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.category_id = c.category_id
),
approved_returns AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT ON (r.item_id)
        r.item_id
    FROM returns r
    WHERE r.status = 'approved'
    ORDER BY r.item_id, r.return_date DESC
),
category_totals AS (
    SELECT 
        ci.category_name,
        SUM(ci.quantity) AS total_items_sold
    FROM category_items ci
    GROUP BY ci.category_name
),
category_returns AS (
    SELECT 
        ci.category_name,
        SUM(ci.quantity) AS total_items_returned
    FROM category_items ci
    JOIN approved_returns ar ON ci.item_id = ar.item_id
    GROUP BY ci.category_name
)
SELECT 
    ct.category_name,
    ct.total_items_sold,
    COALESCE(cr.total_items_returned, 0) AS total_items_returned,
    ROUND(COALESCE(cr.total_items_returned, 0)::DECIMAL / ct.total_items_sold, 4) AS return_rate
FROM category_totals ct
LEFT JOIN category_returns cr ON ct.category_name = cr.category_name
ORDER BY return_rate DESC;
